  "keyword": "WIN",
  "template_id": "UUID",
  "is_active": true
}
```
Response:
```json
{
  "id": "UUID",
  "created_at": "ISO8601"
}
```

`GET /api/triggers?post_id=INSTAGRAM_POST_ID`
```json
[
  {
    "id": "UUID",
    "keyword": "WIN",
    "template": { /* template object */ },
    "is_active": true
  }
]
```

### Template Management
`POST /api/templates`
```json
{
  "content": "Congrats! You won!",
  "media_url": "https://storage.example.com/prize.jpg"
}
```

