### Health Check
`GET /bot/health`
```json
{
  "status": "ok",
  "last_check": "ISO8601",
  "queued_messages": 5
}
```

### Configuration
`GET /bot/config`
```json
{
  "active_triggers": [
    {
      "post_id": "INSTAGRAM_POST_ID",
      "keyword": "WIN",
      "template": { /* template object */ }
    }
  ]
}
```

